    {
      "name": "Magic Allergy",
      "type": "feat",
      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Immediately after a creature within 30 feet of the gremishka casts a spell, the gremishka can spontaneously react to the magic. Roll a [[/r d6]] to determine the effect:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">1-2.</span> The gremishka emanates magical energy. Each creature within 30 feet of the gremishka must succeed on a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">10</span> Constitution saving throw or take 3 ([[/r 1d6]]) force damage.</p></p><p><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">3-4.</span> The gremishka surges with magical energy and regains 3 ([[/r 1d6]]) hit points.</p></p><p><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">5-6.</span> The gremishka explodes and dies, and one swarm of gremishkas instantly appears in the space where this gremishka died. The swarm uses the gremishka's initiative.</p></p></div>",
